Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fred tech
des:
The Frederick, MD tech community is growing and becoming more active than ever. Use this skill to find upcoming events you can attend to learn, get involved, and support your local tech community.

Simply ask Alexa:

“Alexa, ask Fred Tech when is the the next meetup?”

or for a specific group:

“When is the next python meetup?”

This skill was designed and built by 4Thought Technologies, LLC, in support of the local Frederick tech community.

If you encounter any problems or have feedback that you want to share, please feel free to send an email to support@4thoughttech.com.

Note: We’re currently only looking for events from a selection of the local Frederick tech Meetup groups. If you know of other groups to add please contact us.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
